# Angular Exam Cheat Sheet (Angular 17–19)
Author: Sarah Adler

====================================
BASICS
====================================

## Component
יחידת UI בסיסית.

```ts
@Component({
  selector: 'app-header',
  standalone: true,
  imports: [],
  templateUrl: './header.component.html',
  styleUrl: './header.component.scss'
})
export class HeaderComponent {}
Standalone Components (חדשני)
✔ אין AppModule
✔ כל קומפוננטה מנהלת את ה-imports שלה

ts
Copy code
standalone: true,
imports: [NgClass, NgStyle]
Binding (מאוד חשוב)
Property: [value]

Event: (click)

Two-way: [(ngModel)]

html
Copy code
<img [src]="imgUrl">
<button (click)="save()">Save</button>
<input [(ngModel)]="name">
====================================
DIRECTIVES (חדש וישן)
ngClass
html
Copy code
<div [ngClass]="{ active: isActive }"></div>
ngStyle
html
Copy code
<div [ngStyle]="{ 'background-image': 'url(' + img + ')' }"></div>
@if (חדש – מחליף *ngIf)
html
Copy code
@if (isLoggedIn) {
  <p>Welcome</p>
}
@for (חדש – מחליף *ngFor)
html
Copy code
@for (item of items; track item.id) {
  <div>{{ item.name }}</div>
}
====================================
COMPONENT COMMUNICATION
Parent → Child (@Input)
ts
Copy code
@Input() title!: string;
html
Copy code
<app-child [title]="'Hello'"></app-child>
Child → Parent (EventEmitter)
ts
Copy code
@Output() closed = new EventEmitter<void>();
this.closed.emit();
html
Copy code
<app-child (closed)="onClose()"></app-child>
Service Communication (מומלץ היום)
ts
Copy code
@Injectable({ providedIn: 'root' })
export class DataService {
  data$ = new BehaviorSubject<string>('init');
}
====================================
OBSERVABLES & RXJS
Observable
זרם נתונים אסינכרוני.

ts
Copy code
users$: Observable<User[]>;
async pipe (מומלץ)
html
Copy code
<div *ngIf="users$ | async as users">
  {{ users.length }}
</div>
Operators נפוצים
ts
Copy code
map, filter, tap, switchMap
====================================
FORMS
Reactive Forms
ts
Copy code
form = new FormGroup({
  name: new FormControl(''),
  email: new FormControl('')
});
patchValue
עדכון חלקי של טופס

ts
Copy code
this.form.patchValue({ name: 'Sarah' });
====================================
ROUTING
Router Navigate
ts
Copy code
this.router.navigate(['/home']);
Route Params
ts
Copy code
this.route.params.subscribe(p => p['id']);
Query Params
ts
Copy code
this.route.queryParams.subscribe(q => q['token']);
====================================
HTTP
HttpClient
ts
Copy code
this.http.get<User[]>('/api/users');
this.http.post('/api/save', data);
====================================
ANGULAR MATERIAL (Angular 19)
✔ לא צריך MaterialModule
✔ מייבאים לקומפוננטה

ts
Copy code
imports: [MatButtonModule, MatIconModule]
html
Copy code
<button mat-mini-fab>
  <mat-icon>menu</mat-icon>
</button>
====================================
STYLING
BEM (מקובל ועדכני)
lua
Copy code
.block {}
.block__element {}
.block--modifier {}
SCSS טיפ חשוב
scss
Copy code
left: -9px; // חובה יחידה!
====================================
ICONS
Font Awesome
להוסיף פעם אחת ב־index.html:

html
Copy code
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
Devicon (טכנולוגיות)
html
Copy code
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/devicon.min.css">
שימוש:

html
Copy code
<i class="devicon-angularjs-plain colored"></i>
====================================
COMMON MISTAKES (נופלים במבחן!)
❌ import מ־node_modules ידנית
✔ תמיד:

ts
Copy code
import { NgClass } from '@angular/common';
❌ left בלי px
❌ mat-Mini-Fab (שגוי)
✔ mat-mini-fab

❌ לשים <link> בתוך HTML של קומפוננטה
✔ רק ב־index.html

====================================
EXAM TIPS
✔ Standalone > Modules
✔ @if / @for > *ngIf / *ngFor
✔ async pipe > subscribe ידני
✔ Services להעברת מידע
✔ קוד ברור ופשוט

====================================
ALLOWED SEARCH DURING EXAM (לא AI)
https://angular.dev

https://angular.dev/api

https://stackoverflow.com

https://developer.mozilla.org

https://rxjs.dev
